body.string: {"caslibUri": "/casManagement/servers/cas-shared-default/caslibs/Public", "documents": ["Oh yes, the, uh, the Norwegian Blue. What's wrong with it?", "I'll tell you what's wrong with it, my lad. He's dead, that's what's wrong with it!", "No, no, he's uh,...he's resting.", "Look, matey, I know a dead parrot when I see one, and I'm looking at one right now.", "No no he's not dead, he's, he's resting! Remarkable bird, the Norwegian Blue, isn't it? Beautiful plumage!", "The plumage don't enter into it. It's stone dead."], "version": 1, "language": "en"}
